{"tid":2439239,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際專題：縫隙中傳真相 fb直播抗爭  緬游擊記者 守住數碼前線","createTime":"2021-03-09T06:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T06:09:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0d4f1237a278529bd04ef4a91084bf9bba3ee9","tid":2439239,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:09:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/VRKE6PSNI5DD7OTWY2OFA3A7GI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FVRKE6PSNI5DD7OTWY2OFA3A7GI%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy3d5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=704dad03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FVRKE6PSNI5DD7OTWY2OFA3A7GI%2F&h=3985c94a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/VRKE6PSNI5DD7OTWY2OFA3A7GI/</a><br />\n<br />\n等有人覆一覆再繼續 fb直播抗爭 <br />\n緬游擊記者 守住數碼前線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M_AxIhd2acStHHU_2h-1-lOhnPA=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/343FYTYKZNASJDZNSVXRD4AZPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM_AxIhd2acStHHU_2h-1-lOhnPA%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F343FYTYKZNASJDZNSVXRD4AZPI.jpg&h=0916babb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■仰光一名男子被槍所傷，在場人士立即拍下作紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「哪怕只能上傳一張相」<br />\n<br />\n緬甸記者從來不好當。三年前路透社記者因揭露羅興亞屠殺判囚，國務資政昂山素姬力指記者犯法；到今年2月軍事政變，傳媒又與示威者同受壓迫，上周六名記者遭起訴「散播假消息」。不過，艱險中仍有「游擊記者」勇於留在現場，穩守抗爭數碼前線，直播抗爭真相。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英語文宣 盼國際關注支援<br />\n<br />\n對上一次緬甸發生軍事政變是2003年，塔倫從泰這一年入行成為記者。18年後軍人再次奪權，現職民間資助通訊社「新時代」的他即趕回仰光辦公室，帶走幾樣必需品就鎖門，自此沒有再回去，跟九個同事以街頭為編採室，用手機經facebook直播全國示威實況，哪怕每次只能上傳一張照片、十數秒的片段。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook在緬甸等同於互聯網代名詞，5,300萬人口中有一半是用家，是大眾傳播的最後防線。2月22日舉行最大規模全國示威，三個本地傳媒機構在平台做了65場直播，「新時代」其中一段影片成為當天大熱，有18.5萬次瀏覽。平民、社運人士和抗爭者也加入採訪行列，軍警2月20日在第二大城市曼德勒開槍射死兩人，靠現場市民以多角度記錄事件，甚至出動無人機，路透社等外國媒體都靠轉發這些影片，了解現場情況。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：彩虹旗飄揚 「不想走回頭」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jIh6QDEsGDQ0CRPBBOFbtLvwmoA=/802x583/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QHMFOIYGENGEHIEG5BK2PUJFQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjIh6QDEsGDQ0CRPBBOFbtLvwmoA%3D%2F802x583%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQHMFOIYGENGEHIEG5BK2PUJFQI.jpg&h=c2a49bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■19歲抗爭少女鄧家希中彈身亡，引起公憤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壓抑恐懼 拍下死亡一刻<br />\n<br />\n雖已不是首次經歷軍事政變，塔倫從泰承認這次特別心驚膽顫：「情況是我們遇過最惡劣。」無國界記者說緬甸新聞自由排名自2018年連年後退，2月政變以來當局打壓力度更大，緬。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n公民記者承受的壓力亦不下於專業記者。現場有業餘攝影師坦言，要極力抑壓。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n第二個難題是網禁。政變後facebook一度被封鎖，以阻遏反對派傳訊；傳媒和。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eIlK8-f03rR_Cx1n0yqzBKIi42w=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LS5LNUN5RFACXBYTQL3SD667L4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeIlK8-f03rR_Cx1n0yqzBKIi42w%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLS5LNUN5RFACXBYTQL3SD667L4.jpg&h=a165b44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■為打壓抗爭者，軍政府發射催淚彈驅趕巿民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LnxMc5Pn7KkXvjtwyQHV2_VhkSI=/802x496/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2WTLFWDNYJCHTGWT7QRLRCM5DE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLnxMc5Pn7KkXvjtwyQHV2_VhkSI%3D%2F802x496%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2WTLFWDNYJCHTGWT7QRLRCM5DE.jpg&h=136c046d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■緬甸自軍事政變以來，觸發全國各地示威活動，以抵抗極權重臨。"}]}